---
title: Mediterranean Beef and Zucchini Ribbons with Pan Blistered Tomatoes and Almonds
description: Who needs pasta when you've got zucchini ribbons!? Tender-crisp zucchini ribbons tossed in a creamy tahini sauce accompany pan blistered cherry tomatoes in this quick and delicious dish. Crispy ground beef gets a Mediterranean personality and a generous garnish of toasted sliced almonds.

